b'Exchange'
b'Exchange'
b'ACCC provides Exchange email as a premium email and calendaring service available to faculty and staff. This premium service ensures a flawless integration with Outlook enhancing your management of calendar, email, contact, task, and note integration. Exchange has superior speed with large mailboxes, and much more up-to-date and functional web interface. Mobile computing is made easy with native support for Windows Mobile smart phones. Mobile devices are supported by using Exchange Active Sync, available on all major mobile manufacturers (Apple, Android, Windows, BlackBerry).'
b'We currently provide the cloud based version of Exchange, which is known as Exchange Online.\xc2\xa0 All newly hired employees are automatically provisioned with Exchange Online accounts.'
b'Faculty'
b'Staff'
b'IT'
b'ACCC'
