b'Blackboard Collaborate'
b'Blackboard Collaborate'
b'Blackboard Collaborate Web Conferencing\xc2\xa0is a virtual learning environment to facilitate real-time online learning. This Web conferencing system is accessed through Blackboard Learn and empowers Blackboard Learn instructors and TAs to create individual (and repeat Web Conferencing sessions) on their own with out requesting a session to be created or activated.\xc2\xa0'
